description: The construction of blocks ranging from 2 storeys plus roofspace to 6 storeys incorporating balconies and courtyards on part of Silwood Estate (Phase 4C), North of Silwood Street SE16, comprising a total of 146 residential units, 30 one bedroom, 85 two bedroom and 1 three bedroom self-contained flats, 19 three bedroom, 10 four bedroom and 1 five bedroom houses, together with the provision of 86 car parking and 146 bicycle parking spaces, associated landscaping, refuse stores and new highway works.
